## Checklist (new environment)

- [ ] Schema applied from `Latest_Schema_Post__Blob_Claude_12.sql` (per-table `*_id_seq`)
- [ ] INSERT file imported (ordered or renumbered)
- [ ] `sync_all_table_sequences.sql` executed on **this** database
- [ ] `sync_spring_batch_sequences.sql` executed if batch tables have rows
- [ ] Backend deployed with per-table `@SequenceGenerator` and `allocationSize = 1`
- [ ] Verify `sequence_generator` absent; per-table `last_value` ≥ `MAX(id)`; create one test row via app
